sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Router as TGIS Router (Rust)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC TLS/mTLS
    participant HTTP as TGIS Router (Rust)<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant Shard0 as Python Shard 0<br/>UDS plaintext
    participant ShardN as Python Shard N<br/>UDS plaintext
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation (gRPC)
    Client->>KServe: gRPC request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    KServe->>Router: Forward<br/>gRPC/8033, TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate request<br/>(max tokens, seq length)
    Router->>Router: Tokenize input<br/>(HuggingFace tokenizer)
    Router->>Router: Batch queue<br/>(continuous batching,<br/>queue jumping)
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill RPC<br/>gRPC/UDS, plaintext
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
    Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL allreduce<br/>29500/TCP, plaintext
    ShardN->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
    Shard0-->>Router: Prefill result
    loop NextToken loop (until EOS or max_new_tokens)
        Router->>Shard0: NextToken RPC<br/>gRPC/UDS, plaintext
        Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
        Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL allreduce
        Shard0-->>Router: Next token
    end
    Router-->>KServe: gRPC response
    KServe-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: Streaming Text Generation (gRPC)
    Client->>Router: GenerateStream RPC<br/>gRPC/8033, TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate + Tokenize
    Router->>Shard0: Prefill RPC<br/>gRPC/UDS
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
    Shard0-->>Router: First token
    Router-->>Client: Stream first token
    loop Each subsequent token
        Router->>Shard0: NextToken RPC<br/>gRPC/UDS
        Shard0->>GPU: CUDA forward pass
        Shard0-->>Router: Token
        Router-->>Client: Stream token
    end

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: Health Check (HTTP)
    Client->>HTTP: GET /health<br/>HTTP/3000
    HTTP->>Shard0: Health RPC<br/>gRPC/UDS
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA alloc test
    GPU-->>Shard0: OK
    Shard0-->>HTTP: Healthy
    HTTP-->>Client: 200 OK
